{"tid":1833203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post] 1月26號 香港人必須彌補四年前嘅錯誤","createTime":"2020-01-21T17:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T15:09:29.000Z","uid":174174,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"79ecff1a986474119e9de57996d031fbb8fe0bbd","tid":1833203,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T17:16:22.000Z","msg":"2016年<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民主黨出聲明譴責暴力，表示同呢班「暴徒」完全無關，要求徹查襲擊警員嘅\b手足，指警員開槍可以理解<br />\n香港大部分媒體，包括蘋果、立場都將魚蛋革命定性為暴動<br />\n仲有，大部分瞓咗、扮瞓、鬧暴力解決唔到問題嘅香港人</span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EkMogP1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEkMogP1.png&h=61ed99db&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2020年<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">我哋高呼「和勇不分，齊上齊下」、「光復香港，時代革命」，接受以武制暴嘅行動鋼領，認定天琦為國家總統，半信半疑咁畀泛民一次入議會嘅機會。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R0Oeorj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0Oeorj.jpg&h=48444ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今日，我哋係咪欠一班犧牲咗嘅魚革義士，勇武先驅一句對唔住、多謝？<br />\n係咪應該還返佢哋一個公道？<br />\n係咪應該向極權展示我哋不割蓆嘅決心？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jm45vdQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjm45vdQ.jpg&h=6fcd6740&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YXcOs0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYXcOs0w.jpg&h=00cc5108&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vAPts0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvAPts0w.jpg&h=c05219b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RhsVSsc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRhsVSsc.jpg&h=c19d93bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港獨立，民族自強<br />\n只有兩國，才有兩制<br />\n脫支解殖，主權在民</span>"},{"pid":"6ca01d0e8b1617f281f418aaae74d456eef030ff